commit.message:
call.c (print_z_candidates): Do print viable deleted candidates.

	* call.c (print_z_candidates): Do print viable deleted candidates.
	(joust): Don't choose a deleted function just because its worst
	conversion is better than another candidate's worst.

From-SVN: r160808
